cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.PF. 

The paper deals with the analysis of Age of Information (AoI) in discrete time queueing systems. cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely category as AoI is a measure of information freshness. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also likely categories as the paper deals with queueing systems and their analysis. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper uses mathematical techniques to derive expressions for peak and average age. cs.PF (Probability) is another possible category as the paper deals with stochastic processes.
